31
00:02:25,879 --> 00:02:26,639
One army

32
00:02:26,759 --> 00:02:27,879
wiped out six states!

33
00:02:32,525 --> 00:02:33,560
This is

34
00:02:34,250 --> 00:02:35,240
the majesty of the Lord of North Liang,

35
00:02:35,750 --> 00:02:37,360
