Xu Xiao.

36
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:38,650
(Xu Xiao, the Lord of North Liang)

37
00:02:38,650 --> 00:02:39,600
If it were not for him,

38
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:40,900
the world

39
